{"tid":2320512,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［黑警群組］機場警爆群組再多一警染疫 屬確診警密切接觸者獲安排家居隔離 9日8警中招","createTime":"2020-12-11T01:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T03:47:55.000Z","uid":239336,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ca3caa7bc0a2868788c12a5eebee605693fc35","tid":2320512,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:25:51.000Z","msg":"近日接連有警員染疫，警方公佈再多一名駐守機場警區的男警長初步確診，他是早前確診的3名同樣駐守機場的警員緊密接觸者，他獲安排家居隔離，昨晚（10日）隔離期間感到不適，今日（11日）初步確診，本港9日內已有8名警察染疫，機場警區染疫警亦增至4名。此外，衞生防護中心資料顯示，柴灣已婚警察宿舍2座5日內，再多一名四旬婦確診武漢肺炎，這兩名患者都有機會是警嫂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前確診的駐守機場警區3名染疫男警，分別為41歲警長、32歲警員及28歲警員，日前不適，12月7日求醫，8日晚上初步確診。衞生防護中心在9日的疫情記者會指，其中1人確診，但拒絕透露其確診編號；10日公佈的患者名單顯示，一名在12月6日發病的41歲男子、第7189號個案，住油塘油美苑淑美閣。油美苑是紀律部隊員工宿舍，單位主要分配予警務處，其次為消防處等部隊。第7189號個案可能就是9日確診的41歲男警長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/44LQKHUZ6VENTL2NS2LJ3XDUIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2F44LQKHUZ6VENTL2NS2LJ3XDUIQ%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=9aeb70f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2F44LQKHUZ6VENTL2NS2LJ3XDUIQ%2F&h=d877169d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/44LQKHUZ6VENTL2NS2LJ3XDUIQ/</a>"},{"pid":"5faf64f92f09fa12aa73d5d1648a4811997a2743","tid":2320512,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea2c05cf3231f8267dc65c1ae969d4b8cb01996","tid":2320512,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/h