g.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2F44LQKHUZ6VENTL2NS2LJ3XDUIQ%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqcFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=9aeb70f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2F44LQKHUZ6VENTL2NS2LJ3XDUIQ%2F&h=d877169d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/44LQKHUZ6VENTL2NS2LJ3XDUIQ/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:15:31.000Z","msg":"公務員唔係在家工作咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73d3dac6844f30f591518b2ec24772774775e84","tid":2320512,"uid":179775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:15:41.000Z","msg":"光頭警長劉澤基，在微博上「呼應」屈穎妍，大罵請病假護士是「魔鬼」、「垃圾」，「不用懷疑了，這班逃兵醫護在請病假前，已經表明心迹。<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">可能有一日他們病倒了，才知今日自己的所作所為，才知道作為病者的感受。</span></span>但說真的他們明白感受也沒有用，壞了心腸的醫護怎樣變也是魔鬼一隻。 根本就是垃圾，他們的行為影響了一直在前線拼命的醫護英雄」。"}]}